						<div class="postbody">fclose can fail if a signal interrupts the call, so just because you run a fflush, you fclose aren't safe from failing
<br />
<br />i would say; just leave it there, or place an assertion on eof if you want to debug it more easily
<br />
<br />edit: ehum, forgot to mention that a log entry might be a good idea <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /></div>

